>Crossire's font directory</ulink
></entry>
				<entry
>Several fonts available from the Crosswire Bible Society Ftp site.</entry
></row>
	
				<row
><entry
><ulink url="ftp://ftp.netscape.com/pub/communicator/extras/fonts/windows/"
>Bitstream CyberBit</ulink
