>You will see this dialog, which allows adding and removing buttons from the main toolbar of &bibletime;. The order of the can also be changed. </para>
	<mediaobject>
		<imageobject>
		<imagedata fileref="ss_configtoolbar.png" format="PNG"/>
		</imageobject>
